ource/Colin_Jost\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He jokingly provided an update of his medical issues during achat with NBC's Mike Tirico, telling the veteran broadcaster, \\\"I am not on three different medications - four if you include Pina Coladas.\", \"from\": 1848, \"to\": 2047, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1919, \"end\": 1922, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9998610186791771, \"rank\": 7.710532103112502e-05, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}, {\"begin\": 1925, \"end\": 1936, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Tirico\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mike Tirico\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Tirico\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Tirico\"}, {\"begin\": 2034, \"end\": 2038, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rui_de_Pina\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.619060653928336e-15, \"text\": \"Pina\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rui_de_Pina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rui_de_Pina\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My new goal is to have as many infections as there are Olympic Events.\\\"\", \"from\": 2048, \"to\": 2119, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Colin Jost says he woke up Tuesday with an ear infection... in addition to the staph infection on his foot.\", \"from\": 2121, \"to\": 2228, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2121, \"end\": 2131, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colin_Jost\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Colin Jost\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colin_Jost\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colin_Jost\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My new goal is to have as many infections as there are Olympic 